---
title: Paid Booking Flow With Protection
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant TG as Telegram
    participant GW as bot-gateway
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant BK as booking-service
    participant PAY as payment-service
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant NOT as notification-service

    User->>TG: choose booking flow
    TG->>GW: update
    GW->>Redis: rate limit + duplicate update check
    GW->>Redis: save FSM state

    GW->>BK: signed GET /locations
    Note over GW,BK: HMAC + X-Request-Id + replay check
    BK-->>GW: locations

    GW->>BK: signed GET /resources and /slots
    BK-->>GW: resources and free slots
    GW->>TG: show confirmation

    User->>TG: confirm paid booking
    TG->>GW: callback
    GW->>PAY: signed POST /invoices
    PAY->>PG: create SlotHold, PendingInvoice, PaymentSaga
    PAY->>Redis: publish notification.send send_invoice
    Redis->>NOT: consume notification.send
    NOT->>TG: sendInvoice

    User->>TG: pre_checkout_query
    TG->>GW: pre_checkout_query
    GW->>PAY: signed POST /pre-checkout
    PAY->>PG: verify PendingInvoice and active SlotHold
    PAY-->>GW: ok
    GW->>TG: answerPreCheckoutQuery ok

    User->>TG: successful_payment
    TG->>GW: successful_payment
    GW->>PAY: signed POST /successful-payment
    PAY->>PG: update invoice and saga
    PAY->>Redis: publish stream:payment.completed

    Redis->>PAY: consume payment.completed
    PAY->>BK: signed POST /bookings with idempotencyKey payment:invoiceId
    BK->>Redis: acquire slot lock
    BK->>PG: transaction create Booking and BusySlot
    BK-->>PAY: booking created
    BK->>Redis: publish stream:booking.created
    PAY->>PG: PaymentSaga completed
    PAY->>Redis: publish notification.send booking confirmed
    Redis->>NOT: consume notification.send
    NOT->>TG: send confirmation

    alt booking-service fails during payment completion
        PAY->>PG: PaymentSaga failed or awaiting_booking
        PAY->>Redis: message stays pending for retry
    end
